          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The letter calls upon the Biden administration to update its guidance on how it handles federal student debt bankruptcy cases, including by identifying cases where the borrower faces “undue hardship” in repaying their debt as a result of disability or financial circumstances.",
